HELP
==============
1. Manage Playlists
We have 2 levels of playlist (Main & Sub)
You can create whatever you want with the right icon of your subject.

- Right Click on hierachy of the playlist
- Click on New Playlist menu, 
- Fillup the form as you see
- Click Save

2. Manage Playlist files
Please follow for following way:
- Select the playlist you want to save file path
- You need to open the browser or network share folders to copy or drag the files drop 
- Drop files or Right Click paste the file paths to the playlist file panel
- You've done

3. Copy the files from playlist to any media or explorer
- Select the playlists
- Select files from playlist file panel
- Drag or Copy the files
- Drop or paste to the explorer as well

Currently not support copying the whole playlist